   "Back to home" goes back to activate, not homepage. User is STUCK.

2. FALSE EMAIL — Success says "Check jmtrades1990@gmail.com for your login link."
   No email is sent. No email service configured. User waits forever for nothing.

3. SIGN-IN BROKEN — No account created during signup. No password set. Can't log in.

4. DEMO DOESN'T PLAY — /demo either 404 or shows static page. No interactive simulator.

5. PRICING TOGGLE — Monthly/Annual buttons don't switch prices.

6. WAITLIST — "Join waitlist" form doesn't save or confirm.

7. MISSING PAGES — /product, /pricing (full page), /docs, /contact, /privacy, /terms,
   /blog, /blog/*, /industries/* — all either 404 or broken.

8. APP SYSTEM — /app/* doesn't exist at all. No onboarding, no dashboard, no settings.

9. NO SEO — Zero Google results. No sitemap. No robots.txt.

10. NO ERROR PAGES — Bad routes show raw Next.js errors, not styled 404.


# ═══════════════════════════════
# ARCHITECTURE RULES
# ═══════════════════════════════

1. Public page.tsx = Server Component. No "use client". No useEffect. No supabase.
2. Interactive widgets = separate "use client" island files with mount guard:
   ```tsx
   'use client'
   import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'
   export default function Widget() {
     const [mounted, setMounted] = useState(false)
     useEffect(() => { setMounted(true) }, [])
     if (!mounted) return <div className="h-16 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl animate-pulse" />
     return <div>...</div>
   }
   ```
3. Dynamic import for anything using window/document/localStorage at render:
   `import dynamic from 'next/dynamic'`
   `const X = dynamic(() => import('@/components/X'), { ssr: false })`
4. Auth in middleware.ts only. Only protect /app/* routes.
5. Forms: save localStorage first → try API (silent catch) → show success.
6. npm run build after EVERY file. Zero errors.
7. No page may ever show "Verifying session." or blank screen.


