Primary btn: bg-white text-black rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition
Secondary: border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-300 rounded-xl hover:border-zinc-500
Input: bg-zinc-800/50 border-zinc-700 rounded-xl focus:border-zinc-500
Cards: bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-6
Accents: Blue #3B82F6 lead, Green #22C55E appt, Red #EF4444 urgent, Purple #A855F7 outbound, Orange #F59E0B follow-up


